"-p|--print"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"将响应输出到控制台（适用于脚本或非交互式模式）。可访问所有工具，包括 write 和 bash（默认：false）"
,
"en"
:
"Print responses to console (for scripts or non-interactive use). Has access to all tools, including write and bash. (default: false)"
}
}
,
"--output-format"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式（仅在 --print 模式下生效）：text | json | stream-json（默认：\"text\"）"
,
"en"
:
"Output format (only works with --print): text | json | stream-json (default: \"text\")"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式"
,
"en"
:
"Output format"
}
}
}
,
"--stream-partial-output"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以独立文本增量流式输出部分内容（仅在 --print 且为 stream-json 格式下生效）（默认：false）"
,
"en"
:
"Stream partial output as individual text deltas (only works with --print and stream-json format) (default: false)"
}
}
,
"-b|--background"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"后台模式启动（启动时打开 Composer 选择器）（默认：false）"
